Gerard Ribas: Example Common
=================

This is the readme file for example-common project.

This project it will be for persistence and business layer. 

You can see at the moment the persistence layer using my other project es.gerardribas.persistence that it has an Abstract Dao with all the common database accessors. 

What is in this package
=======================

You have only 2 packages:

	--src
		--es.gerardribas.example.common.dao (Interfaces of some DAO examples)
		--es.gerardribas.example.common.dao.impl (Implementation of som DAO examples)
		--es.gerardribas.example.common.domain (Domain Objects refereds in Database)
		
	--test
		--es.gerardribas.example.common.dao (Testing all the DAO implemetations)

This run's? Let's try it!
=========================

Remember! You need previously installed this dependency: 
	<dependency>
		<groupId>es.gerardribas</groupId>
		<artifactId>persistence</artifactId>
		<version>SOME VERSION...</version>
	</dependency>

Thanks for watching